Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.99,0:00:08.81,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哥哥 我要給她換衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.84,0:00:11.93,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哦 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.60,0:00:25.55,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}剛才愛理打來了電話 說是和前輩家裡聯繫了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.43,0:00:28.92,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是嗎 那太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.07,0:00:34.82,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}櫻乃可以去睡了 接下來由我看著就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.48,0:00:36.01,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.14,0:00:46.08,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不要勉強
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.80,0:00:47.39,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.97,0:01:06.54,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}美羽前輩 你一個人太過努力了

Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.59,0:02:58.69,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這裡是?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.63,0:03:02.45,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 新吾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.97,0:03:06.44,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這樣啊 我…

Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.18,0:03:18.55,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\pos(1095,580)}{\pos(980,560)}{\3c&HB58E00&}{\fn方正综艺_GBK\fs40\fad(500,300)}相同顏色的兩人

Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.76,0:03:14.82,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.74,0:03:21.57,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}早上好 新吾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.90,0:03:24.83,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.07,0:03:27.31,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}還想多看看你的睡臉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.76,0:03:28.39,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.27,0:03:33.69,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}身體怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.40,0:03:36.77,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 好很多了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.54,0:03:38.53,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.42,0:03:40.16,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不會
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.24,0:03:43.96,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.35,0:03:45.05,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.83,0:03:52.60,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}對了 我去給你倒杯水
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.50,0:03:55.44,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.86,0:04:24.30,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.70,0:04:26.68,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}喂 媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.99,0:04:32.01,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那今天就在家裡好好休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.32,0:04:34.23,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}動物就交給我們好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.89,0:04:38.50,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 但要發生了什麼就聯繫我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.65,0:04:45.15,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這個是前輩的手機號碼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.88,0:04:46.41,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.04,0:04:47.93,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.49,0:04:51.57,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但今天就交給我們 你好好休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.13,0:04:53.69,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}身體最重要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.19,0:04:55.43,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好…的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.39,0:04:59.37,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}昨天沒能聯繫你 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.34,0:05:02.32,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我不知道紗凪的手機號碼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.27,0:05:05.54,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我怎麼可能告訴你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.91,0:05:09.71,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真是的 怎麼會把前輩交給你這樣的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.89,0:05:11.63,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}得後悔一輩子了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.09,0:05:15.19,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 真想早點見到美羽前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.59,0:05:18.24,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}今天讓她回去休息了 你沒辦法見到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.69,0:05:20.01,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我當然知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.36,0:05:28.57,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}新吾 美羽 吃午飯了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.74,0:05:29.23,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊

Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.61,0:05:31.75,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}美羽前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.05,0:05:35.41,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒 前輩 為什麼在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.50,0:05:41.65,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}對不起 不管怎樣都很在意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.21,0:05:43.07,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.25,0:05:47.72,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我馬上就回去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.82,0:05:53.26,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你真是的

Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.25,0:05:59.34,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.16,0:06:06.97,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是個很好的人 你們覺得怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.43,0:06:08.30,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}幹得好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.90,0:06:10.12,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.62,0:06:11.78,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.61,0:06:17.14,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要養的話只養雌性的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.16,0:06:24.05,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那這樣的話 新吾和美羽怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.17,0:06:28.83,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}必須要分離才行了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.31,0:06:34.50,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.15,0:06:36.05,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.00,0:06:45.00,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}太好了 美羽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.07,0:06:48.32,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}會有人好好疼愛你的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.38,0:06:54.70,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}老師 這孩子就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.50,0:06:58.21,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.30,0:07:06.73,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我也得回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.76,0:07:12.87,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好的 回去就好好睡覺
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.69,0:07:32.36,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}別哭了 美羽已經不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.09,0:07:38.69,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}拜託你 不要再哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.56,0:07:40.71,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}寂寞了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.06,0:07:44.81,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}原來一直都是在一起的 肯定會寂寞的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.32,0:07:49.06,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我們回去以後 它又只剩下一個人了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.25,0:07:52.78,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}最好能早點找到新吾的飼主
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.10,0:07:55.96,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}安潔多去問問看別人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.59,0:07:57.94,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我們也去問吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.67,0:08:01.52,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 我來養
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.90,0:08:02.53,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.10,0:08:04.89,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你在說什麼 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.07,0:08:05.87,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我想養
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.13,0:08:06.84,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.03,0:08:11.68,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這麼說起來 前一段時間美羽前輩說不能養是因為?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.99,0:08:14.74,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒關係的 又不是什麼大事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.07,0:08:15.70,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.76,0:08:16.46,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.03,0:08:20.36,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我說養就養了 就沒人贊成我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.84,0:08:25.20,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}安潔認為 要是小紗凪的話很讓人值得放心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.59,0:08:27.59,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 安心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.06,0:08:31.59,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是啊 我是沒有反對的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.04,0:08:33.95,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是… 真的沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.57,0:08:36.52,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這和你沒關係吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.04,0:08:37.87,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}愛理呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.39,0:08:41.60,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}紗凪要是說可以的話 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.67,0:08:42.86,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}全員一致同意了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.52,0:08:46.62,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那今天開始我們就好好相處吧 新吾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.78,0:09:04.69,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}新吾 今天晚上一起睡覺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.89,0:09:06.92,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}也一起洗澡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.46,0:09:11.46,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}新吾的話 我的全部都可以讓你看的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.87,0:09:14.05,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}喂 新吾好H啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.50,0:09:16.82,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎麼聽起來像我很壞一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.30,0:09:19.50,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒 為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.22,0:09:24.03,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我又不是對你說 是對新吾說的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.80,0:09:25.30,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}唉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.96,0:09:29.50,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}需要準備的東西好多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.02,0:09:32.94,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}洗手間套裝 食物還有裝水的容器
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.11,0:09:36.16,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}修甲器 還需要玩具吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.05,0:09:40.24,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你真的是很喜歡新吾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.69,0:09:41.99,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 最喜歡了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.22,0:09:44.83,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不過事先說明 我喜歡的可不是你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.17,0:09:46.15,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是的 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.48,0:09:47.67,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.73,0:09:51.83,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哦 對了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.25,0:09:52.99,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.54,0:09:57.14,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}明天有事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.83,0:09:58.37,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.05,0:10:00.21,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}如果沒事的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.76,0:10:02.21,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}稍微等下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.23,0:10:04.31,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是美羽前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.63,0:10:05.19,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.67,0:10:08.35,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你好 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.37,0:10:15.27,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}交換號碼了 你知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.01,0:10:19.31,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我知道了 那明天午飯後
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.34,0:10:22.82,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}美羽前輩說什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.76,0:10:27.21,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}說是想對昨天的事情道謝 招呼我去她家做客
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.77,0:10:30.02,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.54,0:10:31.86,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.45,0:10:35.78,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}覺得有些緊張 該怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.07,0:10:39.22,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你可別想些不知廉恥的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.53,0:10:41.42,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我才不會想那些事情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.62,0:10:44.49,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要是對美羽前輩做什麼奇怪的事 我一定會殺了你的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.02,0:10:46.46,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}都說不會了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.02,0:10:49.32,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}明天她家人好像也在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.70,0:10:51.23,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}該說是不會做呢 還是做不了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.60,0:10:53.61,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不 說起來就是不會去做的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.86,0:10:54.59,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不會做的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.51,0:10:59.92,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}對了 紗凪去過前輩家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.31,0:11:00.87,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.59,0:11:05.11,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}她家人是什麼樣的人 有兄弟姐妹嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.55,0:11:27.19,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}別拘束 放鬆就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.83,0:11:29.81,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.54,0:11:35.69,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}對了 美羽前輩身體怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.15,0:11:38.70,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 完全好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.31,0:11:40.27,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.73,0:11:44.46,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那時候對新吾說了 真的是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.96,0:11:46.96,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不 怎麼會呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.39,0:11:50.76,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個 我現在在烤餅乾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.19,0:11:53.12,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那之前 你先和孩子們玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.64,0:11:57.67,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哦 誒…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.07,0:11:59.30,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}等…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.49,0:12:01.66,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.83,0:12:13.05,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}瓜生新吾
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.22,0:12:14.52,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.25,0:12:19.71,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}前幾天幫了美羽 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.06,0:12:22.36,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不 不會
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.79,0:12:26.11,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我一直從美羽那裡聽說新吾的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.00,0:12:30.18,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}說有個比她年紀小的男生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.26,0:12:35.45,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要是願意的話 下回和我一起過夜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.63,0:12:36.19,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.72,0:12:37.31,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.21,0:12:42.49,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不… 好漂亮的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.84,0:12:46.88,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真不愧是美羽前輩的姐…姐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.37,0:12:49.93,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}她可以 我就不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.14,0:12:52.97,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不是的 請冷靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.56,0:13:00.24,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}對不起 就是想確認幫助美羽的是什麼樣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.72,0:13:02.76,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.29,0:13:04.91,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是我放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.35,0:13:07.86,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要是新吾的話 看起來可以放心拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.26,0:13:10.51,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒 拜託什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.16,0:13:12.33,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}新吾
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.71,0:13:19.74,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}美羽是個喜歡逞強 什麼都攬在自己身上的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.03,0:13:25.73,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 那個我也有感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.70,0:13:34.28,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個孩子 小時候養的貓死掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.66,0:13:37.24,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這就成了她心中的陰影
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.10,0:13:41.53,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}感情太深了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.23,0:13:46.88,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}連自然終老的動物 都覺得自己負有責任
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.35,0:13:54.67,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}新吾 能在她身邊支持著她嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.93,0:14:05.67,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我明白了 我會盡可能待在前輩身邊的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.25,0:14:09.84,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}謝謝你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.71,0:14:18.48,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那… 我和新吾什麼時候結婚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.69,0:14:19.44,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.49,0:14:23.17,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}等等 你在做什麼呢 媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.00,0:14:25.54,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.75,0:14:35.12,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}還以為是姐姐呢 原來是母親啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.66,0:14:36.57,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.98,0:14:37.86,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不 不會
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.14,0:14:39.97,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}很好的母親呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.23,0:14:42.43,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒 你喜歡人妻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.84,0:14:44.34,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不是的了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.73,0:14:46.18,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.44,0:14:47.59,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.98,0:14:50.88,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}算了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.31,0:14:51.83,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.72,0:14:53.54,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.81,0:14:56.55,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}烤得好 烤得很好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.81,0:14:57.72,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你為什麼在這
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.14,0:15:00.53,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}試毒啊 試毒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.69,0:15:01.99,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我才沒有放毒藥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.00,0:15:05.42,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那可不行 那麼可怕的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.58,0:15:06.60,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.49,0:15:09.90,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那新吾 就慢慢來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.36,0:15:14.75,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要好好相處啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.20,0:15:16.72,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}別太過分了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.83,0:15:22.78,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真的是對不起了 新吾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.51,0:15:26.84,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}能看到和平時不一樣的前輩 我很高興呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.59,0:15:30.11,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真是不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.46,0:15:41.31,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}新吾真的好容易讓動物親近呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.02,0:15:44.33,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒 是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.29,0:15:48.30,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}小熊喵對新吾不也很親近嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.42,0:15:52.74,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我沒有養過貓
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.22,0:15:57.70,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但覺得美羽新吾和這些孩子都很可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.81,0:15:59.78,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.86,0:16:03.54,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}能加入喵咪部 真的是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.19,0:16:04.86,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.77,0:16:08.04,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}和美羽前輩關係也變好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.33,0:16:10.20,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.19,0:16:14.57,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我也很高興能和新吾關係變得親近
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.59,0:16:16.42,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.16,0:16:28.52,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}今天真的是很謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.32,0:16:30.91,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}還拿了禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.98,0:16:34.20,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不 該道謝的是我才對
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.81,0:16:38.47,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}下回櫻乃也能一起來就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.95,0:16:41.14,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是的 我會轉告她的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.33,0:16:46.35,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那… 社團再見
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.89,0:16:48.34,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}再見
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.23,0:16:57.99,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}給櫻乃打個電話吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.00,0:17:04.61,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.96,0:17:06.49,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}手機嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.88,0:17:08.43,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}稍微等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.62,0:17:10.65,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}麻煩您了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.09,0:17:17.32,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}媽媽 幫我抓住加林和托莫
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.64,0:17:19.28,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.44,0:17:23.14,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊新吾 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.34,0:17:29.63,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}新吾 是這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.50,0:17:34.64,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.12,0:17:39.33,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}明天要怎麼面對前輩才好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.64,0:17:44.92,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}請不要太在意 像平常那樣對待就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.87,0:17:47.70,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.07,0:17:56.03,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}新吾 如果這樣就道別 可能會這麼一直尷尬下去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.05,0:18:00.86,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}再一次送你到公園可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.55,0:18:06.80,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真的很多事 太對不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.64,0:18:09.62,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}為什麼前輩要道歉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.25,0:18:13.06,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個… 沒想到會有那樣的事情發生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.82,0:18:15.62,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我什麼都沒看到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.32,0:18:20.06,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}還不如說看到的好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.03,0:18:24.39,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我看到了 全部都看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.60,0:18:25.61,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.17,0:18:29.44,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}到底怎麼說才好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.80,0:18:31.76,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}新吾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.05,0:18:32.66,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.09,0:18:35.78,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}明天開始也好好相處吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.29,0:18:37.45,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.80,0:18:39.65,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.36,0:18:42.77,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但有件事我想拜託你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.19,0:18:44.93,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.90,0:18:49.86,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}無論什麼事都不要逞強 要和我商量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.51,0:18:52.61,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}難得在一個社團裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.02,0:18:55.46,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}希望你也能依賴我一些
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.10,0:18:57.96,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}謝謝 新吾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.56,0:18:59.76,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我答應你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.04,0:19:15.73,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.03,0:19:17.99,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}早上好

Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.81,0:19:26.15,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和貓生活手冊

Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.44,0:19:26.32,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}前輩她家怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.04,0:19:27.89,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你指什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.41,0:19:30.22,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒做什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.70,0:19:32.08,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}當然沒做了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.54,0:19:35.10,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}理應如此了 別說得好像自己很了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.53,0:19:37.55,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是的是的 對不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.30,0:19:41.86,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不過 我和新吾可是非常恩愛的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.36,0:19:42.88,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.26,0:19:46.72,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}很不錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.38,0:19:49.89,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒 拍得真不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.29,0:19:54.72,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}想要這張照片嗎 特別地我可以送給你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.03,0:19:58.01,Comment,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\fad(300,500)\pos(640,534)}若想獲得紗凪的待機圖片 請在節目結束之後登陸本動畫官網♪ 免費向智能手機開放下載
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.07,0:19:55.94,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.73,0:19:57.42,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.84,0:20:04.46,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒…

Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.10,0:20:08.21,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.50,0:20:10.99,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.62,0:20:14.28,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}腹部長肉了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.97,0:20:18.21,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就算不這麼做 已經很瘦了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.59,0:20:21.19,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}喂 好像自己看過的語氣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.25,0:20:21.63,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.14,0:20:25.21,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒看到 什麼都沒看到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.55,0:20:27.88,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒錯 新吾沒有做錯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.55,0:20:34.16,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.25,0:20:36.92,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}對了 小紗凪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.40,0:20:40.16,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}聽新吾說你收養了那隻小貓
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.05,0:20:42.90,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}擅自就決定了 真對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.13,0:20:46.51,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不會 只要小紗凪沒關係那就沒關係了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.91,0:20:51.23,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}然後 多餘的玩具如果需要就拿去好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.75,0:21:00.90,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}給你 前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.96,0:21:03.67,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}謝謝你 新吾
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.96,0:21:05.22,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不用客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.02,0:21:16.63,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}小紗凪 這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.31,0:21:19.93,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.95,0:21:25.57,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}紗凪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.58,0:21:32.46,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}愛理
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.93,0:21:35.94,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.88,0:21:37.46,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.46,0:21:44.68,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒 這是怎麼回事了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.59,0:21:46.91,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}發生什麼了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.68,0:21:48.54,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.16,0:21:52.99,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}瓜生?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.29,0:21:58.23,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}紗凪…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.12,0:22:01.88,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}
